short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sorare MLB Jet - Injury report & projections for better choices

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SorareMlbJet is the essential extension to succeed in the game Sorare, a fantasy baseball game (www.sorare.com/mlb/).
This addon adds injury information and projections for MLB players.
This will allow you to optimize your choices and avoid selecting injured players.

Posted on:
- The list of your cards
- Past, current and future lobby
- When composing your team
- On the auction market and manager sales
- On the player sheet
- On the squad roster

Information: 
All data added by this extension comes from SorareJet website.
